OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FOfsted's initial response to the death
OL,8,Fof headteacher Ruth Perry appeared
OL,9,F"defensive and complacent", an
OL,10,Findependent review has concluded.
OL,12,FDame Christine Gilbert, who led the
OL,13,Findependent learning review, said the
OL,14,Fculture of the education watchdog
OL,15,Fneeds to be "more open" if Ofsted is
OL,16,Fto fully learn from the tragedy of Mrs
OL,17,FPerry's death.
