OL,4,Cheadteacher's death looked 'defensive
OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,8,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,9,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,10,Fhighest rating of "outstanding" to its
OL,11,Flowest rating ` "inadequate" ` over
OL,12,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,14,FA coroner concluded the Ofsted
OL,15,Finspection in November 2022
OL,16,F"contributed" to Mrs Perry's death.
OL,18,FDame Christine, a former Ofsted chief
OL,19,Finspector, led the review in response
OL,20,Fto the coroner's Prevention of Future
OL,21,FDeaths report from Mrs Perry's inquest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
