OL,4,Cheadteacher's death looked 'defensive
OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FThe report, published on Tuesday,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Looking back, Ofsted's initial
OL,9,Fresponse appears defensive and
OL,10,Fcomplacent rather than reflective and
OL,11,Fself-critical.
OL,13,F"This lack of awareness served to make
OL,14,Fthe coroner's findings all the more
OL,15,Fshocking for Ofsted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
