OL,3,COfsted's first response to
OL,4,Cheadteacher's death looked 'defensive
OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FIt added: "If Ofsted's obvious
OL,8,Fdetermination to learn from the
OL,9,Ftragedy of Ruth Perry's death is to be
OL,10,Ffully realised and sustained, the
OL,11,Fboard must ensure that the culture of
OL,12,Fthe organisation is more open."
OL,14,FThe watchdog has come under greater
OL,15,Fscrutiny after the death of Mrs Perry.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Ofsted announced a series
OL,18,Fof reforms to England's education
OL,19,Finspectorate following its Big Listen
OL,20,Fpublic consultation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
