OL,3,COfsted's first response to
OL,4,Cheadteacher's death looked 'defensive
OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FThe review noted that the criticism of
OL,8,FOfsted in recent years has had an
OL,9,Fimpact on the morale of some
OL,10,Finspectors.
OL,12,FIt said: "Some current HMIs reported
OL,13,Fno longer telling people they met that
OL,14,Fthey worked for Ofsted and were
OL,15,Fworried about being on social media
OL,16,Ffor fear of personal vilification.
OL,18,F"They had received some advice on
OL,19,Fpersonal safety from their managers
OL,20,Ffollowing the tragedy and some had
OL,21,Fsought individual help.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
