OL,4,Cheadteacher's death looked 'defensive
OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FMrs Perry's sister, Professor Julia
OL,8,FWaters, said: "Dame Christine
OL,9,FGilbert's learning review is highly
OL,10,Fcritical of Ofsted's culture and
OL,11,Fpractices in many places.
OL,13,F"It highlights how Ofsted's response
OL,14,Fto my sister's death appeared
OL,15,Fdefensive and complacent. She reveals
OL,16,Fa culture that has allowed inspectors
OL,17,Fto come across as remote and
OL,18,Finfallible, with an unfair power
OL,19,Fbalance between inspectors and those
OL,20,Fthey inspect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
