OL,5,Cand complacent'
OL,7,FSir Martyn Oliver, chief inspector of
OL,8,FOfsted, said: "I'm immensely grateful
OL,9,Fto Dame Christine Gilbert for
OL,10,Fconducting an independent and rigorous
OL,11,Finspection.
OL,13,F"Because of her knowledge she's
OL,14,Fclearly been able to go very deeply
OL,15,Finto Ofsted and produced for me a
OL,16,Freally reflective and useful report
OL,17,Fgoing forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
