OL,7,F"That work cannot be carried out in
OL,8,Fisolation by the inspectorate. It must
OL,9,Fbe carried out in partnership with the
OL,10,Fprofession, and we stand ready to play
OL,11,Four part in building a fairer, more
OL,12,Fhumane inspection system."
